HEADWORD: Otocrane
<hw>O"to*crane</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Oto-</ets> +
Gr. <?/ skull.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>The cavity in the skull in
